.head 2 -  Description: Changes:  
21/08/03 (PXD) Replaced full form window with new dialogue box to provide increased functions
21/08/03 (PXD) Changed postcode and phone/fax fields to strings (they are char in the database)
21/08/03 (PXD) Altered report fields and formulas to use strings in place of numerics as above
21/08/03 (PXD) Changed SQL structure for finding desired customer numbers to process
13/10/06 (PXD) Added ABN and ACN to customer details (although ACN does not yet get stored in DB)
